    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • RsaSha256Condition

        public RsaSha256Condition(RSAPublicKey key)

        Constructs an instance of the condition.

        Development Note: This constructor is _not_ package-private because it may be desirable for a party who only has a public-key to be able to create an RSA-SHA-256 Condition. For example, it might be useful to create a condition that some other party, who _does_ have access to the RSA private key, to fulfill the condition.

        パラメータ:
        key - The RSA public key associated with the condition.

      • RsaSha256Condition

        public RsaSha256Condition(long cost,
                          byte[] fingerprint)

        Constructs an instance of this condition from it's corresponding parts.

        This constructor _should_ be primarily used by Codecs, whereas developers should, in general, use the RsaSha256Condition(RSAPublicKey) constructor, or else create an actual fulfillment via RsaSha256Fulfillment.RsaSha256Fulfillment(RSAPublicKey, byte[]) and then generate a condition from that object.

        パラメータ:
        cost - The calculated cost of the condition.
        fingerprint - The calculated fingerprint for the condition.
